<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Lling</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-11-06 09:28:09</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Our 9-hour camp in the store room in the Temple of Droga resulted in Chief Rukgus spawning about 13 times. He  dropped 6 Essence of Dol (the monk 1HB off hand weapon), about 6 Rukgus Stickers (little 6/25 dagger with a few stats - +3 STR and +2 each wis and int), and - I am pleased to say - one Idol of the Thorned. It will sit proudly in my ranged slot and I am a very happy tank.<BR>
<BR>
On the E'ci server, I have seen very few of these. The ones I have seen for sale by the Uber Guilds have asking prices of $40-$50K. I am a poor tank and not a farmer, so I needed to camp my own, with the help of 3 very good friends and guild mates who sat in that dark hole with me almost all day!<BR>
<BR>
This item is AMAZING and I am stunned to see one, let alone own it. I will never sell or trade it. It is worth the camp, IF you can get the spot.<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
