<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Was in Temple of Droga today and talking to a guy who was bored out of his mind camping this thing.  He finally got it after more than 60 hours of camping it.  That's a pretty brutal drop rate.<BR>
<BR>
He was thrilled to death to finally get the idol, and said he figured it would sell or trade around the 50k range.  Considering that I've never even heard anybody mention the item before, it shows you how rare it is.  It does have three stats on it, as mentioned above, too, so this item needs to be corrected.<BR>
<BR>
Wish I had gotten the item myself!  He can trade it for enough stuff or plat to get pretty much anything his little heart desires.  He's a necro, so he won't keep it for his character.</font></td></tr></table>
